General.Name: Talex S.A
General.Description: Talex S.A. provides IT services in Poland. The company offers data center, colocation, cloud computing, business continuity, IT outsourcing, software development, and IT infrastructure integration services. Talex S.A. was founded in 1989 and is headquartered in Poznan, Poland.
